pic1_alt: FiscalSponsorDirectory.org logo. A gray circle with 3 horizontal bars on the right, and 501 inside, meant to represent a C and a stylized 3. A directory of fiscal sponsors nationwide.
pic2_alt: A pie chart of the Breakdown of directory sponsors by number of projects served, updated March 2023. The largest slice is 1-5 projects (138 sponsors), then 16-19 projects (88 sponsors), 20-49 projects (63 sponsors), 50-99 projects (52 sponsors), 100-199 projects (21 sponsors), and 200+ projects (18 sponsors).
